3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the positive definiteness of the Gaussian RBF on a generic metric space, which is a topic related to data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The paper discusses the use of positive definite kernels on manifolds, which is a topic related to numerical analysis. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper mentions the Grassmann manifold, which is a topic related to graphics and computer vision.
